title: This might be a common question for you guys, but will patch 7.23 be out on November 22?
body: I wanted to know and a lot of other people wanted to know when is zoe going to comeout, and from guess from the “every 2 week patch” will patch 7.23 be out on November 22nd?

replies.body: The patches do tend to come out on a loose 2-week cycle, but those dates aren't set in stone for the most part.
